d I started to photograph it,” she adds. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1222.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1222-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A desolate, snow-covered road stretches into the distance, blending seamlessly with the foggy white sky. Telephone poles line the road, creating a sense of isolation and calm in the wintry landscape.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1222-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1222-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1222-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1222.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/93_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm__DSF0315.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/93_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm__DSF0315-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A snowy landscape featuring several bare trees scattered across a vast, white field. The misty atmosphere creates a serene, minimalist scene, with soft, diffused light and pale sky blending with the snow-covered ground.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/93_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm__DSF0315-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/93_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm__DSF0315-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/93_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm__DSF0315-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/93_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm__DSF