xel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1319_RAW_16-bit-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1319_RAW_16-bit-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1319_RAW_16-bit.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/71_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5493.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/71_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5493-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A large flock of birds flying in the sky against a pale, overcast background. The birds are scattered across the image, creating a dynamic pattern with their varying positions and wing spans.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/71_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5493-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/71_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5493-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/71_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5493-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/71_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5493.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/73_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1027.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/73_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1027-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A snowy landscape with large snow-covered pipes barely visible through the heavy snowfall. The background is obscured by a thick white haze, creating a minimalistic and almost monochromatic scene.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/73_Ange