gelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF6693-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/85_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF6693-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/85_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF6693.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1230-2.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1230-2-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A leafless tree stands alone in a foggy, snow-covered landscape. The branches are bare and barely visible through the dense white mist, creating a serene and minimalistic winter scene.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1230-2-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1230-2-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1230-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1230-2.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5502.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5502-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A vast, snow-covered field stretches into the horizon. A flock of small birds flies in the distance against the pale sky, blending with the muted tones of the landscape. Sparse patterns in the snow suggest subtle ground textures.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5502-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5502-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5502-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF5502.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/94_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF2368-Enhanced-NR.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/94_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF2368-Enhanced-NR-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"Silhouette of a bird in flight against a white sky, wings fully outstretched, with faint snowflakes falling around.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/94_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF2368-Enhanced-NR-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/94_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF2368-Enhanced-NR-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/94_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF2368-Enhanced-NR-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/94_AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF2368-Enhanced-NR.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eBoehm used a \u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/2023/11/20/fujifilm-gfx-100-ii-review-pushing-medium-format-boundaries/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eFujifilm GFX 100\u003c/a\u003e for her project, a medium format digital camera, which she says held up well in the extreme conditions. Nevertheless, there were still difficulties. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“The biggest issue was keeping the camera cold,” she explains. “Once the camera acclimated to the freezing temperatures, I couldn’t bring it into a warmer space, like my vehicle, without it fogging up. As a result, I had to keep my vehicle cold, often leaving the windows down to maintain the same temperature as the outside environment.” \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eAnother issue was battery life. In cold weather, batteries simply don’t perform the way they do in optimal temperatures. So, Boehm always had to keep spare batteries inside her jacket and try to keep them warm, or else they too would drain. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eBoehm couldn’t wear a glove on her right hand while taking photos meaning she was constantly having to put her hand back in her pocket that was filled with hand warmers. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“I would put a mitten on while I walked and explored, but not while finding a scene and photographing,” she explains. “Gloves simply don’t work for pressing the shutter.” \u003c/p\u003e\n \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1093.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1093-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A solitary, leafless tree stands in a snowy landscape. Its bare branches spread widely against a pale, foggy sky, creating a stark and serene winter scene.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1093-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1093-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1093-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF1093.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF3839.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF3839-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"A vast, snowy landscape under a cloudy sky, with subtle, blurred details suggesting wind-swept snow and sparse vegetation barely visible through the white expanse. The atmosphere conveys a sense of cold and desolation.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF3839-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF3839-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF3839-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-AngelaBoehm_AngelaBoehm_DSCF3839.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939-800x800.jpg\" alt=\"An open book on a light green surface, displaying a black and white photograph of a flock of birds flying over a grassy landscape. The image captures a serene, minimalist scene with a focus on nature.\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939-800x800.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939-320x320.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939-100x100.jpg 100w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939-300x300.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939-400x400.jpg 400w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939-600x600.jpg 600w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/Copy-of-P1840939.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eBoehm’s resulting book, titled \u003cem\u003e Minus Thirty\u003c/em\u003e, features essays by writers, including Brad Zellar. “The response has been incredible,” Boehm says of her book. The book is available \u003ca href=\"https://hartmann-books.com/en/produkt/angela-boehm-minus-thirty-en/\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e but is selling fast. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eMore of Boehm’s work can be found on her \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/angela.boehm/\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.angelaboehm.ca/\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003ewebsite\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e \u003chr/\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImage credits:\u003c/strong\u003e Photographs by Angela Boehm.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e      \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
